		fi
		Rscript {params.solutionRscript} --ploidyRun2 {input.ploidyDirs[0]} --ploidyRun3 $ploidyRun3 --ploidyRun4 $ploidyRun4 --threshold {params.threshold} --outFile {output} > {log} 2> {log}
		"""
